    • Field Detail

      • regularizationType

        public int regularizationType
        Regularization type. 0: No regularization 1: L1 regularization 2: L2^2 regularization 3: L2 regularization 4: Infinity norm regularization

      • X

        protected Matrix X
        Training data matrix (nExample x nFeature), each row is a feature vector. The data matrix should not include bias dummy features.

      • T

        protected Matrix T
        An n x 1 matrix for the observation time.

      • Y

        protected Matrix Y
        Label matrix for training (nExample x nClass). Y_{i,k} = 1 if x_i belongs to class k, and 0 otherwise.

      • W

        public Matrix W
        Projection matrix (nFeature x nClass), column i is the projector for class i.
